<h1> <%= @cocktail.name %> </h1>

<p> Calories: <%= @cocktail.calories %> </p>

Mixer/s this cocktail contains: 
<ul>
<% @cocktail.mixers.each do |mixer| %> 
    <li> 
    <%= link_to mixer.name, mixer_path(mixer) %>
    </li> 
<% end %> 
</ul>    

Garnish/es this cocktail contains: 
<ul>
<% @cocktail.garnishes.each do |garnish| %> 
    <li> 
    <%= link_to garnish.name, garnish_path(garnish) %>
    </li> 
<% end %> 
</ul>    


Alcohol/s this cocktail contains: 
<ul>
<% @cocktail.alcohols.each do |alcohol| %> 
    <li> 
    <%= link_to alcohol.name, alcohol_path(alcohol) %>
    </li> 
<% end %> 
</ul>    






<h4>Click here for a random cocktail cocktail!<%= button_to "Show me the cocktail", @cocktail, :method => :get %><br>
</h4>


<li>
<% cocktail = Cocktail.all.sample %> 
<%=link_to cocktail.name, cocktail_path(cocktail)%>
</li>